Title: [ANN][ICO] Specular (SPEK) Token / Long Hold Rewards
Body: About Specular (SPEK) Token  Specular or SPEK is an ERC 20 token with limited supply of 8 888 888 tokens. Our team worked together from across the contents to create this platform.  My goal is to take what I learned from the fails of other ICO’s and come up with a Token that will succeed on the exchange.  Name: Specular Symbol: SPEK Platform: Ethereum Total Supply: 8 888 888 Etherscan: 0x7179694a43f5e95a068edea4bf2b3381876765e6  ICO Rounds  Rounds 1 - $0.05 - 100 000 Rounds 2 - $0.06 - 100 000 Rounds 3 - $0.07 - 100 000 Rounds 4 - $0.08 - 100 000 Rounds 5 - $0.09 - 100 000 Rounds 6 - $0.10 - 100 000 Rounds 7 - $0.11 - 200 000 Rounds 8 - $0.12 - 250 000 Rounds 9 - $0.13 - 400 000 Rounds 10 - $0.14 - 500 000 Rounds 11 - $0.15 - 400 000 Rounds 12 - $0.16 - 300 000 Rounds 13 - $0.17 - 200 000 Rounds 14 - $0.18 - 100 000 Rounds 15 - $0.19 - 50 000 Bonus Round - $0.20 Refunded Tokens  Affiliate & Bounty  We will offer 1 level to earn more Spek by referring new users to the platform. You will get 5% from each user who joins via your specific referral URL.  With our easy to use bounty program you can add links to video or articles and receive from 1 to 1500 free tokens.  By inviting your friends to join you will get 25 free tokens for the first user and 5 thereafter.   Holding Concept  We have developed a long hold reward program, the faster you withdraw funds the less you make the longer you hold the more you gain. Let’s say 1500 users sign up and buy tokens, each of these user start staking at 0.3% but lets say 100 investors withdraw, the percentage will then go up to giving investors who hold longer a higher percentage. The more investor’s who leave the higher the percentage for the long holders. This will continue till the last of the 3 million holding tokens are given out.  Please visit our site: https://spektoken.com  Or read full white-paper on our telegram group: https://t.me/SpekToken
